      },
      "date": "2013-05-03 10:05:26.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 1: Looks good to me, but someone else must approve\n\n(6 inline comments)\n\nHow confident are we that this will work correctly with an upgraded filesystem?  How long as seq-NNNNNNNN-lastid existed?  Was it in 2.3 or only 2.4?\n\nWe are _very_ close to finishing 2.4, so need to know ASAP what kind of impact this might have.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
      "_revision_number": 1
    },
