      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 6.4/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/bac4bc30-b6e4-11e2-bd0f-52540035b04c).  Ran 14 tests.  No failures.",
