      },
      "date": "2013-05-07 08:17:28.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: I would prefer that you didn't submit this\n\nOne defect that I see at the end of local_oid_storage_init():\n\n 851              if (rc == 0 && le64_to_cpu(lastid > OBIF_MAX_OID)) {\n\nThe parenthesis around lastid are incorrect. \n\nAlso, it would be good to move the struct local_oid declaration out of the common header into the compat function if it isn't needed anywhere else.",
      "accounts_in_message": [],
